    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything's cooking, cut your<strong> cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then chop roughly</p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> and <strong>grated carrot</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Indian-style salad</strong></p>",
